item.title: Hello New beginnings
item.description: We are back again in youtube Twitter Simple Shortcode .twitter-tweet { font: 14px/1.45 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,"Helvetica Neue",sans-serif; border-left: 4px solid #2b7bb9; padding-left: 1.5em; color: #555; } .twitter-tweet a { color: #2b7bb9; text-decoration: none; } blockquote.twitter-tweet a:hover, blockquote.twitter-tweet a:focus { text-decoration: underline; } Okay so my name is Siddharth and this is my first tweet. — Kumar Siddharth (@SidtechnetYT) November 23, 2020
